    public static enum DBView.RetCode
extends java.lang.Enum<DBView.RetCode>
    Possible returns from all statement methods.

    Possible codes:

    SQL_SUCCESS - Successful SQL Statement/Action.
    SQL_FAILURE - General SQL Failure.
    SQL_NO_DATA - Data does not exists.
